                        <div class="col interest-rate-value-15 text-right">
                            20 Years
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col what-next-box  text-center">
                    <div class="what-next-text">What's Next?</div>
                    <div class="what-next-text-small">Ready to talk about your loan? Fill up the form below and we'll get in touch with you as soon as possible. Or, if you're ready, <span class="green-text"> sign up</span> with us to apply for a loan immediately.</div>
